# =============================================================================
# Local overrides — copy to `.env.local` (gitignored). Do not commit `.env.local`.
#
# SECURITY:
#   • Every NEXT_PUBLIC_* value is bundled into browser JS — never put secrets tokens,
#     private API keys, or credentials in NEXT_PUBLIC_* (they are visible to visitors).
#   • If overrides were leaked, rotate URLs/keys at the provider and update `.env.local`.
# =============================================================================
#
# Copy to `.env.local` to override values from tracked `frontend/.env`:
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
NEXT_PUBLIC_LIVEKIT_URL=ws://127.0.0.1:7880

# Optional — must match backend worker LIVEKIT_AGENT_DATA_TOPIC (default lk-agent-v1):
# NEXT_PUBLIC_LIVEKIT_AGENT_TOPIC=lk-agent-v1
